  <brief_title>A Randomized Comparison of Intraoperative Warming With the LMA PerfecTemp and Forced-air</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Comparison of Intraoperative Warming With the LMA PerfecTemp and Forced-air</official_title>
